</taxonomicName>
LeConte, 1846.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="469" pageNumber="470">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gozis" authorityYear="1875" family="Nomiidae" lsidName="" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" rank="family">Nomiidae</taxonomicName>
des Gozis, 1875: 3. Type genus: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Laporte" authorityYear="1835" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Nomius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Nomius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Laporte, 1835. Note. The spelling of the family-group name based on 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Laporte" authorityYear="1835" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Nomius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Nomius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was emended to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gozis" authorityYear="1875" family="Nomiusidae" lsidName="" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" rank="family">Nomiusidae</taxonomicName>
by the International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature (ICZN 2011) to remove the homonymy with the hymenopteran family-group name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gozis" authorityYear="1875" family="Nomiidae" lsidName="" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" rank="family">Nomiidae</taxonomicName>
Robertson, 1904.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="469" pageNumber="470" type="diversity">
<paragraph pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Diversity.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="469" pageNumber="470">
Six species arrayed in three genera: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sloane" authorityYear="1890" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Laccocenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Laccocenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Sloane (two species in southeastern Australia), 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Laporte" authorityYear="1835" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Nomius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Nomius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(three species), and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="LeConte" authorityYear="1846" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Psydrus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="469" pageNumber="470" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="469" pageNumber="470">Psydrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(one species).
</paragraph>
